<a href="/questions/332742-in-the-chapter-beware-the-gemini-the">In the chapter &quot;Beware the Gemini&quot; the scene with Mr. Curtain ends abruptly, and then shifts to a dorm room with the kids &quot;remembering&quot; a character named Pedalian who we&#39;ve never met before. Is this is a mistake in the book? Can anyone tell me what happens in that scene? The last line I have is &quot;For LIVE, spelled backwards, is EVIL.&quot; And then it jumps after a space break to &quot;As Jillson had explained…”</a>
