<div id="review_2928121865" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2928121865" />
    <a title="Andrea Cox" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/16407549-andrea-cox"><img alt="Andrea Cox" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1619196848p2/16407549.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2928121865?book_show_action=true">Aug 07, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Andrea Cox" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Andrea Cox" href="/user/show/16407549-andrea-cox">Andrea Cox</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780316003957" href="/book/show/2203136.The_Mysterious_Benedict_Society">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16407549-andrea-cox?shelf=2019-2020-tlc-get-rid-of-it">2019-2020-tlc-get-rid-of-it</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16407549-andrea-cox?shelf=estrangements">estrangements</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16407549-andrea-cox?shelf=adventure">adventure</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16407549-andrea-cox?shelf=childrens-books">childrens-books</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16407549-andrea-cox?shelf=mysteries">mysteries</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16407549-andrea-cox?shelf=twins">twins</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16407549-andrea-cox?shelf=zz-challenges-2019">zz-challenges-2019</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16407549-andrea-cox?shelf=2018-2020-100-wonders-spell-outs">2018-2020-100-wonders-spell-outs</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16407549-andrea-cox?shelf=2018-2020-wonderful-world-of-disney">2018-2020-wonderful-world-of-disney</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16407549-andrea-cox?shelf=2019-total-for-the-year">2019-total-for-the-year</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2928121865" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10631354962163828334">The hype is real, y’all! This is perhaps the most intriguing, unique, and creative children’s adventure book I’ve ever read. I’m nearly thirty-two, and I was quite entertained throughout, so I think this book would be a wonderful one for the whole family. It’s super clean too, which makes it easy to read aloud; there’s nothing to worry about filtering out for sensitive ears of any age. I’m eager to track down copies of the rest of the series’ books.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

