<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer18122262806458235168">Trenton Lee Stewart is the author of the award-winning, bestselling Mysterious Benedict Society series for young readers; The Secret Keepers, also for young readers; and the adult novel Flood Summer. He lives in Little Rock, Arkansas. <br/><br/>Letters to the author may be sent to:<br/><br/>Trenton Lee Stewart<br/>PO Box 251358<br/>Little Rock, AR 72205</span>

